{"tid":1802312,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【屌屌】檢討委員會報告","createTime":"2019-12-29T11:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T11:43:15.000Z","uid":184099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c7a96ee0df8d2836cff522b6e7a7c5d1784e81f7","tid":1802312,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:19:13.000Z","msg":"檢討委員會報告<br />\n<br />\n社會暴亂原因：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1， 青少年國民教育不足</span></strong><br />\n（不了解國情，誤解政策含義）<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2， 通識教育出現問題</span></strong><br />\n（通識教育過於鼓勵青少年參與社會運動而非批判性思考）<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3， 家長監督不足</span></strong><br />\n（家庭不和諧，激發年輕人上街發洩）<br />\n4， <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無法有效保護警察個人私隱</span></strong><br />\n（導致警察無法有效執法）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">檢討項目：<br />\n1， 推行國民教育<br />\n2， 改革通識教育<br />\n3， 促進家庭和諧，家長加強監督<br />\n4， 推行【侮辱公職人員罪】，減少激發警員情緒<br />\n5， 提升警員薪金以提升士氣</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我估會係咁"},{"pid":"f33cb76c06bd629399a8498d3a36d9c0e9d8a075","tid":1802312,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:26:22.000Z","msg":"仲有假新聞假消息 政府會加強溝通之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c44b69a6b31223c9a506b6834b767fa72c1e9a09","tid":1802312,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f33cb76c06bd629399a8498d3a36d9c0e9d8a075","tid":1802312,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:26:22.000Z","msg":"仲有假新聞假消息 政府會加強溝通之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:36:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df0e956dd2eccfdeaba9695d10e0f7e21f13995","tid":1802312,"uid":310970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:40:38.000Z","msg":"仲有網絡太自由，要開始禁網"},{"pid":"599f05c08117578844aa25d3a2f215cb015e1941